data.name: bunifuCustomLabel6.Text
data.value: Every button has it's own functionality. Offline Reading works for already captured or dump files with only PCAP Extension.This will only analyze and visualize the HTTP packets. Online Capturing will caputre the live packets on the machine and then analyze and then visualize the traffic FiddlerCore certificate will be installed on user request. Server and Client application is also created if you want to read packet from other machines.

data.name: bunifuCustomLabel4.Text
data.value: Now-a-days computer security is a big issue. As day by day increase in cybercrime, online fraud and data leakage make people feel unsure on internet. As far as online security is concerned forensic investigation is a big step to overcome this issue. HTTP(S) request are data source for forensic investigation. Observing these network traffic can help investigator to understand the root cause of an incident. Analyzing HTTP traffic without any supportive tool is very difficult task. To overcome this issue Hviz(HTTP(S) traffic visualizer) is technique used, which analyze traffic by reconstruct and visualizes the HTTP(S) of individual hosts.
